<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Hello, this is Juhyung Lee.</h4>



<p class="has-text-align-center wp-block-paragraph" style="font-size:19px;line-height:1.9"><em>Leader</em><br /><em>Educator</em><br /><em>Marketer</em><br /><em>Project Manager</em><br /><em>Business Developer<br />PR &amp; Communications Specialist</em></p>



<div class="wp-block-media-text is-stacked-on-mobile" style="grid-template-columns:41% auto"><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img data-attachment-id="310" data-permalink="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/profile_jh/" data-orig-file="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/profile_jh.jpg" data-orig-size="2227,2375" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1593036254&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}" data-image-title="profile_jh" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/profile_jh.jpg?w=281" data-large-file="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/profile_jh.jpg?w=750" width="960" height="1023" src="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/profile_jh.jpg?w=960" alt="" class="wp-image-310 size-full" srcset="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/profile_jh.jpg?w=960 960w, https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/profile_jh.jpg?w=1920 1920w, https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/profile_jh.jpg?w=141 141w, https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/profile_jh.jpg?w=281 281w, https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/profile_jh.jpg?w=768 768w, https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/profile_jh.jpg?w=1440 1440w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
<p class="has-text-color has-normal-font-size wp-block-paragraph" style="color:#734ec8"><strong><em>Early Years</em></strong></p>



<p class="has-foreground-dark-color has-text-color wp-block-paragraph">Born in South Korea<br /><br />Moved to New Delhi, India in 2008<br />Studied at American Embassy School<br />Conducted a Research Project in 8th Grade on &#8220;Women&#8217;s Education and Empowerment&#8221;<br /><br />Returned to Seoul, Korea in 2013<br />Attended Eunkwang Girls&#8217; Highschool<br /><br />Started studying English Education at Hankuk University of Foreign Studies to carry out my vision on Education and Empowerment.</p>
</div></div>



<p class="has-text-color has-normal-font-size wp-block-paragraph" style="color:#93640d"><strong><em>College Years</em></strong></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As a Freshman, I participated in various forums such as the 8th ASEAN-Korea Frontier Forum as the Delegate of Brunei, and numerous debate tournaments in the Korean debate circuit.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As a Sophomore, I have created posters, flyers and promotion videos for the college debate club, HUFS Debate Society as the President of the club.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">From 2018 to 2020, I worked as the Convener of Korea Youth English Debate Tournaments as an intern at DebateForAll and YTN Media Business Center. As a tournament director of ten tournaments, the hands-on experiences and endless passion drove me here. </p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As a Junior, I served as the secretariat of the Model European Union and organized the entire conference in collaboration with  the Delegation of the EU to the Republic of Korea and Access Communications.  As a debater representing South Korea, our team received grand prize at the Debate Contest of Silk-road Universities Network held in University of Bucharest, Romania.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">As a senior, I have continued my career as a Tournament Director at YTN. I was selected as the Top 5 Finalist of the <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/ceo-for-1-month/" target="_blank">CEO For 1 Month</a> Program at Adecco Korea, a Global HR Firm. </p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph"><strong><em>Career</em></strong></p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">In 2020, I joined DATABANK, an AI EdTech Startup with the vision of providing quality education for all. I worked as the Business Developer at <a href="https://www.data-bank.ai">DATABANK</a> till April, 2022.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">I was deeply engaged in new business development in the education industry and account management &#8211; managing partnerships with over 20 universities and high schools in Korea, and sourcing new business opportunities with educational institutions.</p>



<p class="wp-block-paragraph">Continuing my career in the IT industry, I have worked in Microsoft Korea, promoting Microsoft 365 and Copilot for Microsoft 365 through various marketing campaigns and events for Enterprises in Korea. Currently, I am serving as the Marketing Specialist at o9 Solutions Korea. </p>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-css-opacity" />



<h4 class="wp-block-heading has-light-green-cyan-to-vivid-green-cyan-gradient-background">Experience</h4>



<div class="wp-block-media-text" style="grid-template-columns:18% auto"><figure class="wp-block-media-text__media"><img data-attachment-id="3277" data-permalink="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/home/about/img_8466-2-1/" data-orig-file="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_8466-2-1.png" data-orig-size="2000,2000" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="img_8466-2-1" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_8466-2-1.png?w=300" data-large-file="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_8466-2-1.png?w=750" width="1024" height="1024" src="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_8466-2-1.png?w=1024" alt="" class="wp-image-3277 size-full" srcset="https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_8466-2-1.png?w=1024 1024w, https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_8466-2-1.png?w=150 150w, https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_8466-2-1.png?w=300 300w, https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_8466-2-1.png?w=768 768w, https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_8466-2-1.png?w=1440 1440w, https://ceojuhyunglee.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/img_8466-2-1.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure><div class="wp-block-media-text__content">
